item.description: This website is under construction. My current website is here. I’m working from the awesome Academic Theme and modifying content gradually. I’m currently an Associate Professor of Statistics and Sociology at the University of Washington. I’m also a core faculty member in the Center for Statistics and the Social Sciences and a Senior Data Science Fellow at the eScience Institute. I’m also the Editor-elect for the Journal of Computational and Graphical Statistics.
